# Luxury Salon Image Generation Prompts

These prompts are designed for high-quality AI image generators (Midjourney, DALL-E 3, Stable Diffusion). They focus on a "Japanese Modern Luxury" aesthetic with a sophisticated, minimalist, and serene atmosphere.

**Note:** For Midjourney users, copy the prompt including `--ar` (Aspect Ratio) at the end. For other tools, set the aspect ratio in the tool's settings.

## 1. Hero Background ([hero_bg.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/hero_bg.jpg))
**Size**: 1920x1080 (16:9)
**Prompt**:
> Private luxury salon suite, exclusive atmosphere, one styling chair or treatment bed, soft warm dimmed lighting, beige and dark wood tones, modern Japanese aesthetics, relaxing, quiet, privacy, photorealistic, 8k --ar 16:9

## 2. Concept Image ([concept.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/concept.jpg))
**Size**: 600x800 (3:4)
**Prompt**:
> Close up artistic shot of a drop of water on a white orchid petal, soft focus, high key lighting, purity, serenity, spa atmosphere, Japanese aesthetics, macro photography, elegant, sophisticated --ar 3:4

## 3. Gallery Images ([gallery1.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/gallery1.jpg) - [gallery6.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/gallery6.jpg))
**Size**: 400x400 (1:1)
These should be a mix of interior details, treatments, and products.

**Gallery 1 (Treatment Room)**:
> Private luxury spa treatment room, dim lighting, comfortable massage bed with high-quality linens, aroma diffuser, warm and cozy atmosphere, japanese modern style, photorealistic --ar 1:1

**Gallery 2 (Reception/Lounge)**:
> Luxury salon reception area, marble counter, modern japanese flower arrangement (ikebana), soft ambient lighting, elegant furniture, welcoming atmosphere --ar 1:1

**Gallery 3 (Product/Oil)**:
> High-end organic beauty oil bottles arranged on a wooden tray, natural light, blurred background, spa products, essential oils, dried flowers, aesthetic composition --ar 1:1

**Gallery 4 (Staff/Hand)**:
> Close up of a therapist's hands massaging a shoulder (or just hands in a welcoming gesture), soft lighting, professional uniform, clean, relaxing, high quality --ar 1:1

**Gallery 5 (Interior Detail)**:
> Architectural detail of a japanese modern wall, wood texture, soft shadow, minimalist design, calm atmosphere, zen garden view through a window --ar 1:1

**Gallery 6 (Relaxation)**:
> A cup of herbal tea on a glass table in a relaxation lounge, soft sunlight, comfortable chair in background, peaceful afternoon, luxury lifestyle --ar 1:1

## 4. Map Placeholder ([map.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/map.jpg))
**Size**: 800x450 (16:9)
**Prompt**:
> Digital map interface, Google Maps style, flat vector map, light gray background, white roads and city blocks, red location pin in the center, minimalist UI, highly detailed, Tokyo Aoyama area --ar 16:9
